MLX Corp said a subsidiary hastentatively agreed to acquire a sintered friction materialsbusiness in Milan, Italy, from a unit of Abex Corp forundisclosed terms.    The deal will close after obtaining Italian governmentapprovals, expected in late April.    The business, which will operated under the name S.K.Wellman, will become a member of MLX's specialty frictionmaterials group. The business is a manufacturer of high-energyfriction materials for heavy-duty transmissions and clutches. Reuter&#3;